---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Terms of Service | Mango Media"
  description="Read the Mango Media terms of service for website use, inquiries, and general service-related conditions."
  ogImage="/images/branding/mango-og.webp"
>
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-16 pb-20 sm:pt-20 sm:pb-24 lg:pt-24 lg:pb-28">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10">
      <div class="absolute left-[-8%] top-12 h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(254,205,76,0.34),transparent_65%)] blur-2xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute right-[-6%] top-0 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(218,60,120,0.22),transparent_60%)] blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 h-64 w-64 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(1,155,144,0.14),transparent_62%)] blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container-shell">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-black/8 bg-white/80 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--color-text-secondary))] shadow-soft backdrop-blur dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5">
          <span class="inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full leaf-gradient"></span>
          Legal
        </div>

        <h1 class="mt-6 font-nunito text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))] sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
          Terms of Service
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-base leading-8 text-[rgb(var(--color-text-secondary))] sm:text-lg">
          These Terms of Service govern the use of the Mango Media website and general interactions initiated through this site.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pb-20 sm:pb-24 lg:pb-28">
    <div class="container-shell">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl surface-panel radius-brand p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-10">
        <div class="space-y-8 text-[rgb(var(--color-text-secondary))]">
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              Use of This Website
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              By accessing this website, you agree to use it only for lawful purposes and in a way that does not harm Mango Media, the website, or other users.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              Information on This Website
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              Content on this website is provided for general informational and marketing purposes. While Mango Media aims to keep information accurate and current, no guarantee is made that all information is complete, error-free, or up to date at all times.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              Service Inquiries
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              Submitting a form or inquiry through this website does not create a client relationship, service agreement, or guarantee of project acceptance. Any actual engagement for services will be subject to separate agreement, scope, pricing, and approval.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              Intellectual Property
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              Unless otherwise stated, website content, branding, copy, layouts, and design elements on this site are the property of Mango Media and may not be copied, reproduced, or reused without permission.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              Third-Party Links and Services
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              This website may include links to third-party websites or rely on external platforms and tools. Mango Media is not responsible for the content, policies, or operations of third-party services.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              No Warranty
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              This website and its contents are provided on an “as is” and “as available” basis without warranties of any kind, whether express or implied.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              Limitation of Liability
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              To the fullest extent permitted by law, Mango Media will not be liable for any damages arising from the use of, or inability to use, this website or reliance on information presented on it.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              Changes to These Terms
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              Mango Media may update these Terms of Service at any time. Changes will be posted on this page.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              Contact
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              For questions about these terms, contact:
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              Mango Media<br />
              Miami, Florida<br />
              <a
                href="mailto:contact@mangomedia305.com"
                class="font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--color-text))] transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-[rgb(var(--color-mango-pink))]"
              >
                contact@mangomedia305.com
              </a>
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>